value.0: This armor was made from the skin of a bear, enchanted to rival the power and magnificence of the beast. It sports thick fur padding that offers an adequate defense.
Piecemeal or complete armors of this type grant protection equivalent to studded leather or hide.
This is a fine suit of heavy armour bearing the signature of Thargrim from Kakar Runedar.
A shovel is ideal for moving quantities of dirt from one location to another.  Other uses are possible, of course.
